originalText.text: I love Dr. T!!!! I got a tummy tuck and breast lift with doctor T and I’m obsessed with the results. I asked a million questions before the procedure and not once was he annoyed with my questions. During the procedure he was very supportive with my nervous self and the nurses and anesthesiologist was very kind. Best bed side manners ever. After the surgery everyone was helpful. Dr. T and the nurses kept calling me to check up on me. Every time I had a question I would text him and he would reply right away. I am so lucky that I chose Dr. T to be my plastic surgeon.
